{"tid":422763,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我洗唔洗睇下醫生","createTime":"2017-10-03T10:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T14:21:44.000Z","uid":91459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"19108f1cdf6292a6557f1744996b0c8a6d97b417","tid":422763,"uid":91459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"話說小弟三個月前比女飛，個刻灰到pk<br />\n但依家3個月過去左，情緒依然好波折，一時覺得冇野，好睇得開。但每兩星期總會有幾日特別灰，係灰到想跳樓個隻<br />\n我其實好好彩，依段時間入面有好多朋友同家人既扶持，但我一諗到依家自己仲係咁灰，就覺得好對佢地唔住<br />\n我唔敢再煩佢地，唯有上黎開post問下，我三個月仲咁灰係唔係可接受？定係我應該去睇下醫生？好驚成世都係咁"},{"pid":"800771345a702280b68b193fe3323faf9fe252c8","tid":422763,"uid":146139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:57:00.000Z","msg":"呢個世界真係美麗！D空氣真係清新！"},{"pid":"fe6b60038760cc50af3700800c6bffbfb9cedd31","tid":422763,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fb64ec5ec0c97d7d23f96e7b66de97575a3a792","tid":422763,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"唔使 慳番啦<br />\n你條廢柴唔好再曬錢就得"},{"pid":"178689d8a1013e68cf2433cbc3e9070c4d6661c5","tid":422763,"uid":140922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個世界真係美麗！D空氣真係清新！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  苑瓊丹子"},{"pid":"50e71ff693cabe7c89dba007ee6a0ec88055615a","tid":422763,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:11:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44ff21772d97411e41bbad6f3604ca7bbd177811","tid":422763,"uid":91459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中出咗未先？<br />\n中出過洗咩灰<br />\n溝過個又有新閪屌</blockquote><br />\n又係依句&hellip;<br />\n依d野根本唔重要"},{"pid":"8b4f93cd3be0a363add22547dfee5a4ad5414961","tid":422763,"uid":56626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"有理無理睇咗先啦，一陣再灰啲真係醫生都唔想睇"},{"pid":"fbd6f6defe3cc34429c46983b8d24a5e99228247","tid":422763,"uid":83597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7eef04c96bc1944d9898de99398b60ceeefa122","tid":422763,"uid":91459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再靜多幾個月<br />\n就去識下新女仔<br />\n好快又係一條好漢子</blockquote><br />\n都有approach下其他女<br />\n但完全冇意慾去追"},{"pid":"d47b035624b6a4d04ab0907381cc019729eff911","tid":422763,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"時間可以治癒一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49e9a179249878f4179fde5f67124c1c559de95","tid":422763,"uid":85926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"睇醫生冇乜用其實<br />\n<br />\n自己睇得開先有用<br />\n<br />\n利申：三年情緒病"},{"pid":"4c6ebe712ed23f07d1441c1c6ed6c9de5a3bbdb2","tid":422763,"uid":8648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"慢慢啦 時間可以沖淡一切 又或者時間可以俾到你一個逃避既機會 總之慢慢黎 搵啲野搞下 分下心"}]}